icture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When William Greystoke was born about 1158, in Lincolnshire, England, his father, Ranulph Greystoke, was 30 and his mother, Amabel Balliol, was 25. He married Helawise de Stuteville about 1180, in England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1209, in Greystoke, Cumberland, England, at the age of 52, and was buried in Barrow in Furness, Cumbria, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"about 1158–1209":"umbes 1158–1209","1158–1209":"1158–1209","1161–Male":"1161–Surnud","1162–1213":"1162–1213","1142–1226":"1142–1226","1190–1247":"1190–1247","1205–Female":"1205–Surnud","1130–1190":"1130–1190","1135–1204":"1135–1204","1190":"1190","1142":"1142","1130":"1130","1162":"1162","1161":"1161","about 1190 date fits better":"umbes 1190","1205":"1205","1204":"1204","1226":"1226","31 March 1204":"31. märts 1204","1247":"1247","1213":"1213","1158":"1158","1135":"1135","about 1158":"umbes 1158","about 1157":"umbes 1157","1209":"1209","Abt 1180":"umbes 1180","Greystoke, Cumberland, England":"Greystoke, Cumberland, England","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Lincolnshire, England":"Lincolnshire, England",", , , England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Barnard Castle, Durham, England":"Barnard Castle, Durham, England","Furness, Cumbria, England":"Barrow in Furness, Cumbria, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1158–1209":"noin 1158–1209","1158–1209":"1158–1209","1161–Male":"1161–Kuollut","1162–1213":"1162–1213","1142–1226":"1142–1226","1190–1247":"1190–1247","1205–Female":"1205–Kuollut","1130–1190":"1130–1190","1135–1204":"1135–1204","1190":"1190","1142":"1142","1130":"1130","1162":"1162","1161":"1161","about 1190 date fits better":"noin 1190","1205":"1205","1204":"1204","1226":"1226","31 March 1204":"31. maaliskuuta 1204","1247":"1247","1213":"1213","1158":"1158","1135":"1135","about 1158":"noin 1158","about 1157":"noin 1157","1209":"1209","Abt 1180":"noin 1180","Greystoke, Cumberland, Englan